name: Proxy Paige (skinny)
description:
Proxy Paige

Skinny Version

She left us too soon...the slender version, that is. It's possible an eating disorder may have had something to do with it, especially compared to her current "healthier" look. This is my favorite version of Proxy, though, so thats what you get.

From a run of 5000 steps I pulled the 3000 step sample and think it's the most realistic, though to be honest, earlier versions were just as good.

Built on v1.5, as per usual she looks best on all of the nicer Models available here.

Also, if anyone can think of how do replicate her familiar blonde hair with pink highlights, please let me know in the comments. Thanks!

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
